beer.beer_name: Jon Pom Jovi Pomegranate Sour Ale
beer.beer_description: Our Magnificent Mullet fruited sours series is getting even more magnificent with this latest addition! Jom Pom Jovi Pomegranate Sour Ale is bursting with slightly sweet & slightly sour pomegranate! This beer is part of our Magnificent Mullets series. The flavour is short and tart up front, but long and pomegranate-y at the back.
